      "body" : "The `-rpcbind=129.168.0.123:8332` option seems to be ignored when set. I also tried it with `bitcoind.exe`.\n\nNote, that `-rpcallowip=*` triggers an assertion failure:\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/12032350/17629347/22f664fc-60ba-11e6-86d0-9abbec21ab46.png)\n",
